#: ../../source/DualGrid.rst:10 283b07bb1f1f465faa09cd04d56fba9a
msgid "Dual Grid Approach"
msgstr "双网格方法"

#: ../../source/DualGrid.rst:12 8aa39dd3f9454e9b8826035238993b62
msgid ""
"In AMReX-based applications that have both mesh data and particle data, the mesh work and particle work have very "
"different requirements for load balancing."
msgstr "在基于AMReX的应用程序中，既有网格数据又有粒子数据，网格工作和粒子工作对负载平衡有非常不同的要求。"

#: ../../source/DualGrid.rst:15 bbfab4b6e13d4418868b2063a10c6562
msgid ""
"Rather than using a combined work estimate to create the same grids for mesh and particle data, we have the option to "
"pursue a \"dual grid\" approach."
msgstr "与其使用一个综合的工作估计来创建网格和粒子数据的相同网格，我们有选择采用“双网格”方法。"

#: ../../source/DualGrid.rst:18 8fc83b3adf944a3dbab1a0b76c39e0d2
msgid ""
"With this approach the mesh (:cpp:`MultiFab`) and particle (:cpp:`ParticleContainer`) data are allocated on different "
":cpp:`BoxArrays` with different :cpp:`DistributionMappings`."
msgstr "采用这种方法，网格（:cpp:`MultiFab`）和粒子（:cpp:`ParticleContainer`）数据在不同的:cpp:`BoxArrays`上分配，并具有不同的:cpp:`DistributionMappings`。"

#: ../../source/DualGrid.rst:21 e8b19c67c90342dca8cdf0146673f309
msgid "This enables separate load balancing strategies to be used for the mesh and particle work."
msgstr "这样可以为网格和粒子工作使用不同的负载均衡策略。"

#: ../../source/DualGrid.rst:23 99644a0160544c2bb095d075fafc21ba
msgid ""
"The cost of this strategy, of course, is the need to copy mesh data onto temporary :cpp:`MultiFabs` defined on the "
"particle :cpp:`BoxArrays` when mesh-particle communication is required."
msgstr "当然，这种策略的代价是在需要进行网格-粒子通信时，需要将网格数据复制到在粒子`BoxArrays`上定义的临时`MultiFabs`中。"
